XCode 4 Assembler Project Template (Minimal + Standart Project Settings)

Import Standart Settings from com.apple.dt.unit.base, com.apple.dt.unit.Macbase

Create one source file "ProjectName.s"

Write to source file comment, simple example.

Set Project Build Settings: GCC_VERSION = 4.2, LINK_WITH_STANDARD_LIBRARIES = NO

Create Target Build Phases: Source, Frameworks.
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --

About XCode 4 Project Templates:
http://snipt.net/yonishin/about-xcode-4-project-template

Download and move Folder "Assembler Command Line Tool.xctemplate" to
"~/Library/Developer/Xcode/Templates"